# ⚔️ Difference Between sh and bash

| Feature  | sh                  | bash              |
| -------- | ------------------- | ----------------- |
| Type     | Basic shell         | Advanced shell    |
| Features | Limited             | Rich              |
| Arrays   | Not supported       | Supported         |
| Syntax   | Simple              | Powerful          |
| Use      | Lightweight scripts | DevOps automation |

