# 🚀 Role of Shell Scripting in DevOps

## 1. Infrastructure Maintenance

* Automate server setup
* Monitor CPU, memory, disk usage
* Restart services automatically

## 2. Code Management using Git

* Automate git clone, pull, push
* Store scripts in GitHub for version control

## 3. Configuration Management

* Automate cron jobs
* Navigate directories
* Manage application setup

## 4. Monitoring at Scale

* Monitor 1000+ VMs
* Detect high CPU and memory usage
* Identify problematic machines
* Send alerts or notifications

## 5. Automation using Cron Jobs

```bash
crontab -e
```

* Schedule scripts to run automatically
* Example: monitor system every 5 minutes

